00:10:29.735 --> 00:10:31.446
To je Njujork tajms.

00:10:31.446 --> 00:10:33.022
Ali čekajte, čekajte. Čekajte.

00:10:33.022 --> 00:10:34.544
Oh, Gven,

00:10:34.544 --> 00:10:36.087
sećaš li se da sam zaboravio

00:10:36.087 --> 00:10:37.210
ljubičasti marker,

00:10:37.210 --> 00:10:40.165
i nisi mogla da obojiš ovcu?

00:10:40.165 --> 00:10:41.648
Pa, ako nastaviš da čitaš

00:10:41.648 --> 00:10:43.279
počevši od 25 na dole,

00:10:43.279 --> 00:10:44.185
kaže:

00:10:44.185 --> 00:10:45.958
„Oh, usput,

00:10:45.958 --> 00:10:50.270
ovca može ostati prazna."

00:10:50.270 --> 00:10:54.706
(Smeh) (Aplauz)

00:10:54.706 --> 00:10:56.280
Ali čekajte, još jedna stvar,

00:10:56.280 --> 00:10:57.483
još jedna stvar,

00:10:57.483 --> 00:11:00.322
tu je još jedan poslednji deo mozgalice.

00:11:00.322 --> 00:11:04.641
Gven, zahvalan sam na tvojim izborima

00:11:04.641 --> 00:11:06.632
jer ako pogledamo

00:11:06.632 --> 00:11:08.863
prva slova tvojih kombinacija,

00:11:08.863 --> 00:11:11.875
dobijamo C-H-A-O-S za "chaos" (haos)

00:11:11.875 --> 00:11:14.698
i O-R-D-E-R za "order" (red).

00:11:14.698 --> 00:11:16.228
To su haos i red.

00:11:16.228 --> 00:11:17.904
Svi smo napravili red iz haosa.

00:11:17.904 --> 00:11:19.907
Dame i gospodo, kada sledeći put

00:11:19.907 --> 00:11:21.459
budete rešavali mozgalicu,

00:11:21.459 --> 00:11:24.321
bilo da je vezana za život ili posao,

00:11:24.321 --> 00:11:25.752
ili je možda u nedelju ujutru

00:11:25.752 --> 00:11:28.090
za doručkom uz Njujork tajms,

00:11:28.090 --> 00:11:31.932
setite se, vi ste sposobni da rešavate.

00:11:31.932 --> 00:11:33.524
Hvala.

00:11:33.524 --> 00:11:36.844
(Aplauz)

